casebody.data:
The BERGEN COUNTY BAR ASSOCIATION, INC., the Passaic County Bar Association, Inc. and Middlesex County Bar Association, Inc., Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
STATE of New Jersey, and the Supreme Court of New Jersey, Defendants-Respondents. C-163 September Term 2018
081513 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 5, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004353-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
